00:22.397 --> 00:26.192
Look, you can think you know someone
because you've been through shit together.

00:27.318 --> 00:29.237
Or because you came up together.

00:31.865 --> 00:34.659
But to actually know
what's going on in a person's head,

00:35.994 --> 00:37.662
or in their heart, I mean…

00:39.873 --> 00:41.082
You can't know that.

00:42.584 --> 00:43.710
You can't.

00:46.254 --> 00:49.340
Like with me, I mean, people…
people think that they know me

00:49.424 --> 00:52.385
because I made them laugh
or because they've been to a show.

00:56.431 --> 00:58.433
But they don't know
what I did to get here.

00:59.851 --> 01:01.644
Or what it takes to stay here.

01:04.856 --> 01:06.733
When a person's back is against the wall,

01:06.816 --> 01:09.986
and they gotta do whatever they can
to keep from losing what they got…

01:14.699 --> 01:16.910
that's when you get to see
who a person is.

01:19.537 --> 01:21.164
Or what they're capable of.

01:24.042 --> 01:25.752
You know <i>that </i>about someone…

01:27.212 --> 01:28.379
Well, then, maybe…

01:30.590 --> 01:32.801
maybe then you can say that you know 'em.

01:34.469 --> 01:35.595
But then again,

01:36.471 --> 01:37.680
you know <i>that…</i>

01:42.936 --> 01:44.604
maybe you wouldn't want to.

01:52.237 --> 01:55.406
<i>Let's get ready to rumble!</i>

02:03.623 --> 02:06.501


02:06.584 --> 02:08.711
-Right this way, Kid.

02:08.795 --> 02:10.630
<i>Our first guest</i>
<i>is one of my favorites.</i>

02:10.713 --> 02:12.799
<i>-He's been here many times before.</i>

02:12.882 --> 02:16.219
<i>His new film </i>The Anti-verse
<i>is playing in theaters now</i>

02:16.302 --> 02:20.598
