<i>one billion dollars at the box office.</i>

02:20.682 --> 02:22.767


02:22.851 --> 02:26.896
<i>This weekend, he'll be headed back</i>
<i>to his hometown, Philadelphia,</i>

02:27.730 --> 02:29.899
<i>yeah, the City of Brotherly Love,</i>

02:30.859 --> 02:34.612
<i>for the start of his worldwide</i>
<i>comedy tour, "What Did I Tell You?"</i>

02:36.072 --> 02:37.615
<i>We're so lucky to have him here…</i>

02:38.950 --> 02:41.327
<i>…and I'm proud to call him a friend.</i>

02:41.411 --> 02:45.165
<i>Comedy star, TV star,</i>
<i>movie star, entrepreneur, mogul,</i>

02:45.248 --> 02:48.334
<i>philanthropist, dreamboat.</i>

02:49.627 --> 02:51.838
