02:56.176 --> 02:57.385
The Kid.

03:03.099 --> 03:05.018
Thank you. Thank you.

03:08.188 --> 03:11.691
And then we saw S<i>tolen Money.</i>
My wife and I couldn't stop laughing.

03:11.774 --> 03:13.735
