This nigga done been all around the world.

14:52.433 --> 14:55.769
-All right. Showtime.
-Showtime, baby, showtime.

14:56.729 --> 14:58.772
Y'all know how we do,
we go to bring it in.

14:58.856 --> 15:00.608
-Let's get this prayer in.
-Yes, sir.

15:00.691 --> 15:03.527
Here we go. All right, dear Lord,

15:03.611 --> 15:06.322
let these jokes be funny
and the reviews be good. Amen!

15:06.405 --> 15:09.325
-Amen to that, the reviews are good.

15:09.408 --> 15:11.493
The reviews are always good. Okay?

15:11.577 --> 15:13.203
-Go get it!
-Yes, sir.

15:13.996 --> 15:16.081
-I want seconds!
-They're ready?

15:16.165 --> 15:17.750
-They're ready.
-My guy!

15:17.833 --> 15:21.337
All right, you motherfuckers ready
to have a good time tonight?

15:22.504 --> 15:24.506
Wassup, Philly?

15:26.050 --> 15:27.968
Y'all ready to have a good time tonight?

15:28.052 --> 15:30.012
