I can't hear y'all.

15:30.095 --> 15:32.264
I said, y'all ready
to have a good time tonight?

15:36.727 --> 15:38.938
-Fucking unbelievable!
-Dude, it felt so good.

15:39.021 --> 15:41.106
-It did? That was like… Ah!
-So good.

15:42.024 --> 15:44.193
-So good.
-So good.

15:44.276 --> 15:46.445
Your brother and his crew,
they're backstage.

15:46.528 --> 15:48.781
-I gave 'em a wave, they're in the corner.
-Okay.

15:48.864 --> 15:51.909
Okay. Let me just put this
in your head real quick, okay?

15:51.992 --> 15:54.036
This is when Carlton
starts to become Carlton.

15:54.119 --> 15:56.830
VIP room wasn't good enough,
so I made him a V-VIP room.

15:56.914 --> 15:58.666
I don't know what that is. I made that up.

15:58.749 --> 16:02.169
I watch you take baby steps with him,
you don't take them with other people.

16:02.252 --> 16:04.129
Todd, just leave it the fuck alone, man.

16:04.755 --> 16:07.633
-Please, just leave it alone.

16:07.716 --> 16:09.802
I know how to deal with <i>my</i> brother.

16:10.719 --> 16:12.846
-I do.
-Yes, you do. Okay.

16:12.930 --> 16:15.516
I know this Black family politics thing
is tough for you.

16:15.599 --> 16:18.018
