fuck up my life after tonight.

16:29.488 --> 16:30.906
-All right?
-Thank you.

16:32.658 --> 16:34.076
-I love you, man.
-I love you back.

16:34.159 --> 16:34.994
Hey…

16:35.077 --> 16:36.495
