17:54.698 --> 17:55.991
-Have a good night.
-Thanks.

17:56.075 --> 17:57.826
-Congratulations.
-Yeah.

18:01.830 --> 18:03.457
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.

18:04.208 --> 18:05.834
-What up, champ?
