his chaperone over there.

19:03.475 --> 19:04.309
Yeah.

19:04.393 --> 19:06.603
-This is weird for you?
-Look how serious he is.

19:06.687 --> 19:07.855
Say no more. Say no more.

19:07.938 --> 19:11.150
