a weird vibe in here with my guys.

19:11.233 --> 19:14.111
Hey, just gimme a sec, man.
My guy. Thank you.

19:14.194 --> 19:16.989
Okay, is that better?
That better? Are we good?

19:17.072 --> 19:20.033
You need some drinks for that.
I'm on drinks. Let's do this.

19:20.117 --> 19:22.244
Yeah, man, come on. Let's do it.

19:22.327 --> 19:23.662
-Drinks? Drinks?
-Or shots?

19:24.413 --> 19:26.456
-Yeah, that top-shelf vodka.
-Yeah.

19:26.540 --> 19:27.791
Get the vodka on that.

19:27.875 --> 19:29.001
-Hey,
-Yeah.

19:29.084 --> 19:32.671
Real quick, between us, you know
I'm not really trying to drink like that.

19:32.754 --> 19:33.922
I'm six months sober.

19:34.006 --> 19:37.342
Oh, right. As many times
as you done fell off, I forgot.

19:37.426 --> 19:41.221
Yeah, but we can't celebrate without you.
Come on, just a little sip, man.

19:41.305 --> 19:42.973
Just a little sip.

19:43.056 --> 19:46.768
All right. Yeah, this is a toast
to my little brother.

19:47.436 --> 19:49.479
-Always got my back.
-There it is.

19:49.563 --> 19:51.023
-There it is.
-Yes, sir.

19:51.106 --> 19:52.024
My man.

19:57.029 --> 19:58.280
Oh yeah.

19:59.114 --> 20:00.657
Fill 'em up! Fill 'em up!

20:02.784 --> 20:04.661
You know how we do, back-to-back.

20:04.745 --> 20:06.371
-That's right.
-Back-to-back.

20:07.164 --> 20:09.541
-There it is, that's my man!
-Whoa!

20:09.625 --> 20:12.753
What's good, man? Go ahead,
finish that up, man. Quit playin'.

20:12.836 --> 20:15.547
You want us to put a nipple on it?
Come on, man. Drink it.

20:16.423 --> 20:18.717
We could add some salt,
baby bottle, finish that.

20:18.800 --> 20:20.177
Let's go! Get on the level!

20:20.260 --> 20:22.262
-Let's get it.
-Down the hatch with us.

20:24.389 --> 20:26.141
-Hmm? Whoo!

20:29.728 --> 20:32.940
-There he is! My man.
-That's what I'm talking about, boy!

20:33.023 --> 20:35.234
-Yeah! How we used to do!
-We gonna have some fun.

20:35.317 --> 20:37.569
Look, excuse me a second.

20:38.278 --> 20:40.197
Oh, okay. Okay.

20:40.781 --> 20:42.032
Yo, there you go.

20:42.658 --> 20:43.992
Wait, hold, hold up.

20:44.076 --> 20:46.161
We went to see
your latest movie the other day.

20:46.245 --> 20:47.913
We missed half the jokes

20:47.996 --> 20:51.166
'cause C was in there
laughing his ass off.

20:51.250 --> 20:53.543
-Carlton was doing that? Ah.
-Yeah, Carlton.

20:54.461 --> 20:56.880
Wait, he… he didn't tell you he saw it?

20:56.964 --> 20:58.799
Wait, why do you say that?

20:58.882 --> 21:02.344
No, man. He told me,
he said y'all went, had a good time.

21:02.427 --> 21:03.553
He said it was love.

21:03.637 --> 21:05.973
-Yeah, man. It was off the chain.
-Yes, sir.

21:06.598 --> 21:08.141
-Proud of you.
-Stop it, man.

21:08.225 --> 21:10.227
-Don't know what this means to me.
-Come a long way.

21:12.229 --> 21:14.815
I wanna introduce you
to some of my friends.

21:14.898 --> 21:18.110
Thank y'all for coming out tonight.
Much appreciated.

21:18.193 --> 21:20.988
We don't need a club,
I just made one for you right here, baby.

21:22.489 --> 21:24.825
That's right. Ladies, ladies,
you know who this is, right?

21:24.908 --> 21:27.452
-Yeah, we do.
-Go ahead. Introduce yourselves.

21:27.536 --> 21:28.912
Can I take a picture with you?

21:29.788 --> 21:31.999
-Yeah? Thank you.
-Yeah, yeah, yeah.

21:35.252 --> 21:37.504
Ah, I love it. Thank you.

21:38.755 --> 21:39.881
Sorry, that was…

21:43.051 --> 21:45.804
One shot this time. Just one?

21:54.104 --> 21:55.731
-Okay.
-Go.

21:55.814 --> 21:57.232
-Okay.
-Another one.

21:57.316 --> 21:59.318
-Another one, damn. Hold on.
-Yeah.

22:00.277 --> 22:02.404
-There it is.
-Mmm.

22:03.530 --> 22:04.364
So?

22:04.448 --> 22:07.951
It's insane. I can't believe
you got me drinking like this. Shit.

22:08.869 --> 22:11.288
-You're cool. Gimme a second please.
-Okay.

22:11.371 --> 22:12.664
All right. Hey.

22:13.415 --> 22:15.334
I gotta get the fuck outta here.

22:16.209 --> 22:19.004
-You already took a sip, man.
-No. Come on.

22:19.087 --> 22:20.964
Listen, I ain't been this bad in a minute.

22:21.048 --> 22:23.425
I've been… I've been dry for a while.

22:23.508 --> 22:26.219
We gonna keep this shit
between us, all right? All right?

22:26.303 --> 22:30.265
-Besides, I need a wingman.
-You need a wingman?

22:30.349 --> 22:33.602
Yeah, I need a wingman, man.
You can't leave. You gotta stay.

22:35.103 --> 22:36.688
You want me to stay, I'll stay.

22:36.772 --> 22:39.775
But I ain't staying all night.
I ain't doing that.

22:39.858 --> 22:41.693
Not all night. I'll stay for a little bit.

22:41.777 --> 22:42.652
Man.

22:43.236 --> 22:44.237
I love you, man.

22:46.031 --> 22:48.367
