-I love you too.

22:48.450 --> 22:49.326
And, and…

22:50.077 --> 22:53.372
I didn't mean to let you down.
I'm sorry about that.

22:53.455 --> 22:55.665
All of it. All of it.

22:59.002 --> 23:02.422
Hey, maybe tomorrow
we can talk about the money?

23:03.757 --> 23:05.884
I mean, I can save this restaurant, man.

23:06.927 --> 23:08.887
Listen, I hear what you're saying.

23:10.097 --> 23:14.142
But you… you gotta listen to me too,
though, right?

23:14.226 --> 23:15.560
You ain't let me down.

23:16.228 --> 23:18.897
When you let me down?
I ain't never say you let me down.

23:18.980 --> 23:20.232
You keep saying that.

23:20.315 --> 23:21.274
Love.

23:21.358 --> 23:23.902
But you keep saying you <i>need</i> it.

23:23.985 --> 23:25.237
"I need it."

23:25.862 --> 23:27.656
You don't need it. You want it.

23:27.739 --> 23:30.951
It's a big difference between
what you need and what you want.

23:31.660 --> 23:35.080
Maybe this whole thing that happened
and this shit happened for a reason.

23:36.164 --> 23:39.334
It happened to show you.
You know what I mean?

23:39.418 --> 23:42.963
To… to give you
a different look at this shit.

23:43.046 --> 23:46.091
Mm. Yeah, yeah.

23:46.174 --> 23:49.136
Yeah. But we're here
to celebrate you, all right?

23:49.219 --> 23:51.346
-We're celebrating me?
-We celebrate you.

23:51.430 --> 23:52.347
I like that.

23:53.140 --> 23:54.474
Hey, real quick.

23:54.558 --> 23:56.810
I know I'm your wingman,
but answer this question.

23:57.310 --> 23:58.311
Is she cute?

23:59.146 --> 24:01.815
-I think she cute.
-Yeah, she cute, man.

24:11.241 --> 24:13.952
K? K, wake up. Wake up, man.

24:14.035 --> 24:14.911
Wake up.

24:14.995 --> 24:17.247
Wake up. Wake up. Come on. Come on.

24:17.330 --> 24:19.082
Come on, come on, wake up.

24:19.166 --> 24:21.751
What the fuck you doing?
What do you mean, come on?

24:21.835 --> 24:23.295
Get out of my fucking room.

24:23.378 --> 24:25.922
-What the fuck are you doing? What?
-Just come on.

24:26.006 --> 24:28.967
What are you doing, man?
What the fuck are you doing? What?

24:29.050 --> 24:31.595
-What'd you take, K? What'd you take?
-I didn't take shit.

24:31.678 --> 24:34.055
-What did you give her?
-I ain't give nobody nothing.

24:34.139 --> 24:36.183
-What the fuck are you talking about?
-Shit.

24:36.266 --> 24:38.101
What are you-- What's the problem?

24:38.643 --> 24:40.729
-What's the fucking problem?
-We got a situation.

24:40.812 --> 24:42.606
-What situation?
-She dead.

24:43.607 --> 24:45.066
She dead, man.

24:50.697 --> 24:51.823
Fuck you mean, she dead?

24:51.907 --> 24:53.950
How you know she's not breathing?
Did you check her?

24:54.034 --> 24:56.161
Carlton, did you fucking check her?

24:57.204 --> 24:59.331
Oxy. The big ones.

25:00.499 --> 25:02.000
I'm calling a fucking ambulance.

25:03.001 --> 25:04.628
-I'm calling an ambulance!
-No.

25:04.711 --> 25:07.214
Let me call a fucking ambulance.
You just said she--

25:07.297 --> 25:11.009
If you call the ambulance,
they'll call the fucking cops.

25:11.092 --> 25:13.512
They'll call the fucking cops.

25:21.853 --> 25:23.230
<i>She got kids, man?</i>

25:23.313 --> 25:25.273
How the fuck
I know if she got kids?

25:27.734 --> 25:29.986
Did she take a picture of us
while we were there?

25:30.070 --> 25:31.446
Did people see her leave with us?

25:31.530 --> 25:34.533
People saw you leave here,
come in the fucking hotel.

25:34.616 --> 25:35.659
Of course they seen.

25:35.742 --> 25:39.621
Listen, I'm telling you, man.
Your next move better be a smart one.

25:40.121 --> 25:42.457
-I gotta get my phone, man.
-What the fuck you doing?

25:42.541 --> 25:44.417
-I gotta get my--
-Whoa, whoa, whoa.

25:44.501 --> 25:47.587
You think this is some fucking DUI
or something like that?

25:47.671 --> 25:49.798
Some of that bullshit
you put up on Twitter?

25:49.881 --> 25:51.174
Dude, you got a body.

25:52.008 --> 25:54.511
I'm fully aware
of the fucking situation, man.

25:54.594 --> 25:57.222
But at least,
if I get my phone, I'll call Todd.

25:57.305 --> 26:01.226
Todd can come. Todd can help us
figure this shit the fuck out, man.

26:01.309 --> 26:03.186
No, no, no. You can't call your counselor

26:03.270 --> 26:05.772
and have this conversation
over the next fucking weeks.

26:05.855 --> 26:08.400
Dude, you got a dead woman
in your fucking bed.

26:09.025 --> 26:10.026
Next to you!

26:13.238 --> 26:14.281
Fuck.

26:20.495 --> 26:21.705
I fucked up.

26:22.998 --> 26:25.250
I fucked up, man.

26:25.333 --> 26:26.251
Shit.

26:26.960 --> 26:28.878
I got this. I'ma take care of this, man.

26:28.962 --> 26:31.590
What do you mean, you got this?
What do you mean?

26:31.673 --> 26:33.925
Do you understand
what the fuck is happening?

26:34.843 --> 26:39.931
Everything I worked hard for, everything
I bust my fucking ass for is over.

26:40.640 --> 26:42.350
It's a wrap, man.

26:42.434 --> 26:45.562
Throw that shit in the trash.
What the fuck I'ma say to Mo?

26:45.645 --> 26:48.773
How am I gonna explain
this shit to Christian?

26:50.066 --> 26:51.693
I need to call someone

26:51.776 --> 26:54.029
that can… that can help us

26:54.112 --> 26:56.948
and… and really help
figure this shit out.

26:57.032 --> 26:59.451
You need to shut the fuck up.
I told you I got this.

27:02.996 --> 27:04.456
What you gonna do, Carlton?

27:07.792 --> 27:08.877
All right.

27:16.509 --> 27:18.595
We gonna tell the cops
that she was with me.

27:19.471 --> 27:23.224
I was the one that brought her here,
you went in your room, we went in my room,

27:23.308 --> 27:26.353
and then, you know, she OD'ed in my room.

27:26.978 --> 27:28.980
You ain't know nothing about it.

27:29.064 --> 27:33.026
See, that way, like, if the cops gotta
arrest somebody, then they arrest me,

27:33.109 --> 27:35.904
and nobody gonna be suspicious
because I already got a jacket,

27:35.987 --> 27:37.238
you know what I mean?

27:38.114 --> 27:40.575
So, yeah.

27:41.284 --> 27:44.245
This way, we keep you out of it.

27:50.377 --> 27:51.711
That's your plan, C?

27:53.463 --> 27:54.422
Yeah.

27:59.844 --> 28:01.680
They not gonna let you own that.

28:02.722 --> 28:07.060
They would never let you own that,
even if the cops fucking believed you.

28:07.143 --> 28:08.812
The press is gonna spin it.

28:08.895 --> 28:10.980
"It's a dead girl in Kid's room."

28:11.064 --> 28:14.192
That's the headline.
That's what it's gonna say on CNN.

28:15.151 --> 28:18.238
-That's what it's gonna say on CNN.
-Okay, all right.

28:18.321 --> 28:20.115
You come up with a better plan, then.

28:25.453 --> 28:27.872
I shoulda just fucking did
what I was supposed to do, man.

28:27.956 --> 28:29.165
And what was that?

